ndma's illness has healed."],[2933,3004,"Emma,"],[3032,3283,"you are Grandma's Little Lucky Sweetie."],[3366,3546,"My checkup report is out today."],[3654,3804,"I don't know what to expect."],[4145,4283,"Dad will be fine."],[4312,4520,"Dad is going to live a long life."],[5575,5629,"Mr. Hayes,"],[5666,5850,"your medical report is out."],[5862,6070,"But the results are a bit unusual."],[6075,6154,"What is it?"],[6241,6291,"Mr. Hayes,"],[6333,6441,"the tumor in your lungs"],[6462,6600,"has not only stopped growing,"],[6604,6720,"but actually shrunk."],[6737,6841,"It's a medical miracle."],[6845,6983,"And the toxins in your body"],[6987,7116,"have completely vanished."]],"43":[[33,142,"Emma just had to say the word,"],[192,350,"and I recovered without any medicine."],[408,500,"It's truly magical."],[675,733,"Mom,"],[745,1004,"my illness is practically cured, too."],[1112,1270,"That's wonderful."],[1358,1437,"Emma,"],[1608,1750,"you really are Dad's Little Lucky Sweetie."],[1841,1958,"The good news for our family"],[1979,2141,"just keeps coming, one after another."],[2166,2250,"It's endless good fortune."],[2391,2520,"What other good news is there?"],[2541,2595,"Mom,"],[2625,2747,"Sir Quinn has taken Emma in"],[2753,2870,"as his god-granddaughter."],[2895,3008,"Thanks to Emma,"],[3016,3164,"we secured the deal with the Quinn family."],[3171,3254,"Plus,"],[3261,3366,"the Imperial Jade Emma won"],[3367,3483,"at the auction"],[3508,3620,"sold for $400 million."],[3670,3786,"Oh my goodness,"],[3820,3920,"our Emma"],[3920,4040,"is really amazing."],[4112,4220,"Grandma is amazing,"],[4231,4320,"Dad is amazing,"],[4325,4462,"and I'm amazing too!"],[4467,4554,"Everyone in our family"],[4562,4687,"is amazing!"],[5725,5837,"Sister-in-law,"],[5846,6058,"your birthday is the day after tomorrow,"],[6067,6161,"I made a special trip"],[6163,6342,"to bring you a birthday gift."]],"44":[[45,116,"Victor,"],[158,254,"I can't accept"],[261,344,"your gift."],[362,470,"Just take it back."],[