ing is all set."],[1117,1233,"I'll make sure that wild brat"],[1275,1383,"never comes back!"],[1691,1866,"She got me stung all over!"],[2223,2270,"Victor,"],[2300,2441,"Andrew is trying to make peace with us."],[2625,2712,"What do you mean?"],[2740,2893,"Andrew sending us a gift,"],[2910,3069,"isn't that him bowing down to us?"],[3491,3633,"This box,"],[3637,3812,"looks familiar."],[4491,4625,"Don't open it!"]],"49":[[720,804,"Emma,"],[850,995,"staying at the office with me"],[1020,1120,"might get really boring."],[1179,1308,"Do you want Grandma to pick you up?"],[1445,1645,"Dad, I won't be bored."],[1684,1850,"I'll be a good girl"],[1870,2037,"and play with my toys nearby."],[2073,2281,"I won't disturb your work."],[2470,2595,"You're such a good girl."],[2641,2687,"Let's go."],[4279,4400,"You're not as tall as me."],[4762,4829,"Mr. Hayes,"],[4833,4916,"our joint project with"],[4920,5070,"the Quinn Group has run into trouble."],[5091,5170,"What happened?"],[5195,5371,"The development route runs through Mount Cloud,"],[5406,5520,"but during excavation,"],[5566,5777,"workers found waste left by Hakan."],[5929,6020,"What did you say?"],[6044,6137,"The workers are afraid of accidents,"],[6141,6216,"so they've all gone on strike."],[6262,6387,"The project is suspended."],[6437,6570,"Mount Cloud is the only way through."],[6645,6754,"If we have to reroute,"],[6958,7066,"the cost will be too high."],[7146,7222,"Oh no."],[7270,7447,"Dad's in trouble."],[7529,7637,"I also heard that"],[7691,7812,"the Quinn Group"],[7816,7945,"is planning to drop the project."],[8158,8345,"I invested everything I had."],[8425,8566,"If the project is canceled,"],[9079,9275,"the company will lose everything."],[9433,9547,"Dad is such a good person."],[9603,9725,"Good people should be rewarded."],[9829,10037,"This will surely work out."]],"50":[[53,162,"You're such a good person, Dad."],[184,322,"Good things happen to good people."],[322,527,"Everything will work out."],[733,799,"Mr. Hayes,"],[875,1000,"I'm worried Victor"],[1004,1170,"will use this chaos to force you out."],[1583,1704,"I'll call Mr. Quinn."],[2133,2160,"Hello?"],[2162,2203,"Mr. Quinn."],[2223,2279,"Andrew."],[2296,2469,"I have good news for you."],[2473,2556,"Good news?"],[2611,2699,"Isn't it bad news?"],[2734,2834,"Jimmy told me everything."],[2862,3000,"During the excavation at Mount Cloud,"],[3014,3216,"they found waste left by Hakan."],[3279,3375,"It's a difficult situation."],[3441,3504,"I sent experts"],[3508,3658,"to survey the site."],[3681,3754,"They discovered that"],[3758,3845,"the experimental waste"],[3854,4033,"was just a decoy."],[4041,4129,"Mount Cloud"],[4133,4249,"is actually a gold mine!"],[4412,4491,"A gold mine?"],[4525,4587,"That's wonderful!"],[4775,4918,"I never expected Mount Cloud"],[4920,5062,"to be a gold mine."],[5070,5116,"My guess is"],[5120,5295,"Hakan discovered the gold back then"],[5300,5417,"but didn't have time to mine it,"],[5425,5533,"so they used this method"],[5537,5641,"to create a false impression."],[5648,5728,"Mining the gold"],[5775,5912,"will not only save on labor costs,"],[5941,6066,"but we'll also make a fortune."],[6108,6170,"Andrew,"],[6204,6324,"Emma was right."],[6375,6500,"Whoever partners with you"],[6504,6637,"is bound to make money."],[6683,6737,"Mr. Quinn,"],[6783,6920,"I'll come to your office this afternoon"],[6925,7029,"to talk with you in person."],[7577,7701,"Was it Emma who helped me"],[7701,7833,"solve this problem again?"]],"51":[[87,154,"Daddy,"],[160,359,"why do you keep looking at me?"],[527,623,"Because,"],[671,817,"you are just so cute."],[887,951,"And,"],[987,1120,"you're Daddy's Little Lucky Sweetie."],[1227,1279,"Mr. Hayes,"],[1302,1462,"you're beaming with joy."],[1512,1620,"Is the problem resolved?"],[1765,1862,"It's all resolved."],[1904,2029,"There's no lab waste on Mount Cloud."],[2108,2297,"It's a massive gold mine."],[2387,2437,"Mr. Hayes,"],[2441,2554,"your luck is incredible."],[2579,2762,"You turned the tables against all odds."],[2795,2887,"You're just too lucky."],[2983,3037,"That's because"],[3108,3270,"I found a lucky star."],[3416,3573,"Ever since you adopted Miss Emma,"],[3573,3658,"good luck keeps coming."],[3756,3816,"Could it be"],[3858,3987,"that Miss Emma is a lucky star?"],[4158,4225,"Miss Emma,"],[4291,4350,"how about"],[4383,4491,"I bow down to you?"],[4641,4704,"Jimmy,"],[4745,4841,"are you really bowing?"],[4950,5116,"Uncle, I'm just a child."],[5137,5287,"You can't bow to me."],[5345,5429,"Miss Emma,"],[5462,5562,"I have only one wish."],[5633,5725,"I want to be a father."],[5795,5870,"No problem."],[6312,6362,"Jimmy,"],[6412,6504,"you've got some nerve."],[6527,6644,"You dare try to steal my daughter?"],[6667,6754,"Mr. Hayes, Mr. Hayes!"],[6771,6833,"I wouldn't dare claim to be"],[6837,6970,"Miss Emma's father!"],[7031,7129,"Then what do you mean?"],[7245,7366,"My wife and I"],[7368,7488,"have been trying for a baby for two years,"],[7604,7745,"but she still hasn't gotten pregnant."],[7802,7885,"That's why I was hoping"],[7908,8022,"Miss Emma"],[8033,8137,"could bless me with a child."],[8204,8279,"Jimmy,"],[8283,8487,"your wish will definitely come true."],[9102,9158,"Really?"]],"52":[[37,120,"Honey,"],[125,241,"the doctor says I'm pregnant."],[245,350,"It's twins!"],[354,450,"You're gonna be a dad."],[454,550,"What?"],[554,654,"That's great!"],[775,841,"Miss Emma,"],[845,937,"thank you."],[941,1037,"Thanks to your blessing,"],[1041,1175,"my wish really came true."],[1187,1307,"You're welcome."],[1639,1711,"Grandma!"],[1741,1883,"You're such a good girl, Emma."],[1925,2004,"Mom,"],[2016,2137,"what brings you here?"],[2487,2587,"Men looking after kids"],[2591,2687,"are just so careless."],[2716,2841,"You only care about work."],[2887,2962,"Did you forget?"],[2995,3133,"Today we're taking Emma"],[3137,3273,"to buy a pretty dress"],[3279,3412,"for my birthday party."],[3704,3783,"It's my fault."],[3825,3980,"How could I forget that?"],[3991,4054,"You stay busy."],[4058,4158,"I have nothing to do"],[4162,4280,"at home anyway."],[4290,4370,"I'll take Emma"],[4375,4484,"shopping for clothes."],[4509,4559,"Thanks,"],[4562,4616,"Mom."],[4731,4790,"Emma,"],[4845,4933,"- Let's go. - Okay."],[4975,5091,"Bye, Dad."],[5095,5191,"Bye, Jimmy."],[5204,5350,"- Bye. - Bye."],[6491,6637,"You're here."],[7008,7183,"It's all because of that little b*stard."],[7287,7383,"She almost got me beaten to death"],[7387,7561,"by that scumbag Hank."],[7858,7920,"Sharon,"],[7925,7975,"now that"],[8035,8175,"we've kidnapped the brat,"],[8179,8279,"do you think"],[8283,8379,"their family"],[8383,8562,"will really pay the ransom?"],[8566,8704,"She isn't Andrew's"],[8708,8804,"biological daughter."],[8816,8987,"Then let's kidnap the old geezer"],[9050,9154,"as well."],[9225,9379,"If Andrew doesn't pay,"],[9507,9678,"we'll kill them!"],[9741,9787,"Alright."],[9791,9870,"Whatever you say."],[9875,9948,"We'll take them both"],[9954,10062,"and make a fortune."]],"53":[[275,371,"Emma,"],[371,533,"why didn't you want the clothes"],[538,664,"I picked out for you?"],[683,771,"Grandma,"],[771,992,"I already have so many clothes."],[1019,1189,"I can't even wear them all."],[1194,1356,"It would be a waste."],[1364,1443,"Madam,"],[1450,1529,"the Young Miss"],[1533,1620,"is so sensible."],[1687,1745,"Grandma,"],[1750,1914,"today is your birthday."],[1917,2096,"Buying new clothes for you is enough."],[2140,2233,"I also bought"],[2237,2370,"an outfit for Daddy."],[2406,2548,"I miss Daddy."],[2558,2704,"Then I'll take you to see him."],[2704,2747,"Okay."],[2827,2915,"Cathy,"],[2929,3100,"have the manager send all the clothes"],[3104,3212,"Emma looked at to the Hayes family."],[3216,3254,"Yes,"],[3265,3360,"Madam."],[3437,3508,"Let's go, Emma."],[4071,4179,"Emma."],[4290,4540,"I bought you new clothes!"],[4800,4875,"Emma."],[5125,5200,"Come here, Emma."],[5341,5529,"You really are Daddy's sweetheart."],[5561,5670,"You went out shopping,"],[5675,5791,"and still thought of Daddy."],[5883,6070,"Emma is so sweet."],[6083,6220,"She refused to buy clothes for herself,"],[6225,6345,"but insisted on buying for us."],[6412,6525,"That won't do."],[6541,6583,"Emma,"],[6591,6641,"come on."],[6662,6791,"Daddy will take you to buy clothes."],[7070,7133,"Mr. Hayes,"],[7137,7285,"Victor and Brandon are here."],[7290,7469,"They have something important to tell you."],[7548,7670,"Why are they here again?"],[7675,7808,"Kick them out."],[8214,8304,"Andrew!"],[8370,8537,"Something happened at Mount Cloud."],[8558,8712,"You don't know yet?"],[8775,8937,"Something happened at Mount Cloud?"],[9027,9175,"How did you find out before me?"],[9204,9391,"The gold mine there collapsed."],[9408,9531,"Two workers"],[9531,9650,"are trapped inside."]],"54":[[0,120,"Andrew,"],[175,340,"something happened at Mount Cloud."],[344,466,"Don't you know yet?"],[495,641,"Something happened at Mount Cloud?"],[660,800,"How did you find out before me?"],[808,987,"The gold mine over there collapsed,"],[1025,1166,"and two workers"],[1170,1304,"are trapped inside."],[1345,1533,"Those two workers"],[1537,1762,"happen to be relatives"],[1765,1860,"of your Second Aunt's family."],[1875,2020,"I've already notified them"],[2062,2194,"to come to Hayes Group"],[2196,2287,"and make a scene at the gate."],[2300,2400,"Andrew,"],[2441,2562,"you'd better think about"],[2591,2770,"how you're going to fix this."],[2888,2975,"You big bad guy!"],[2979,3125,"You did this on purpose!"],[3258,3350,"Andrew,"],[3354,3562,"as long as you agree to let me in"],[3579,3708,"on the project,"],[3763,3900,"I'll make this trouble"],[3925,4054,"fade away"],[4091,4229,"completely."],[4275,4354,"What do you say?"],[4375,4470,"Andrew,"],[4508,4612,"I didn't kick you"],[4616,4725,"out of the company back then,"],[4729,4879,"which was already generous of me."],[4916,5091,"Don't refuse my offer"],[5095,5233,"and choose the hard way."],[5245,5354,"Are you threatening me?"],[5408,5529,"If I can't have it,"],[5566,5704,"you won't get it either!"],[5775,5887,"Unless"],[5891,6112,"you can get the trapped workers"],[6116,6250,"out safely."],[6295,6370,"Otherwise,"],[6375,6512,"things will get ugly."],[6516,6679,"You won't get away with this."],[6703,6982,"The trapped workers will make it out safely."],[7379,7520,"To secure the partnership,"],[7550,7648,"you bribed the workers"],[7650,7779,"and played with human lives."],[7837,7941,"Victor,"],[7987,8175,"you really deserve to die."],[8250,8316,"Victor,"],[8341,8512,"you're truly out of your mind."],[8545,8662,"The Quinn Group partnership"],[8665,8798,"must not fall into your hands!"],[8908,9000,"Sister-in-law,"],[9066,9158,"as the saying goes,"],[9162,9362,"a wise man submits to circumstances."],[9391,9587,"You wouldn't want to see Andrew"],[9591,9766,"take this little brat"],[9770,9941,"and beg on the streets, right?"],[9995,10220,"Even if I have to beg,"],[10275,10408,"I'll make sure the bad guys"],[10441,10600,"get punished."],[10633,10737,"Andrew,"],[10741,10929,"have you thought it through?"],[10983,11062,"You only get"],[11066,11204,"one chance."]],"55":[[33,116,"Victor."],[183,342,"You're out of your mind."],[454,612,"You people are so evil."],[616,833,"Bad guys never win."],[945,1004,"You little brat."],[1008,1119,"I've put up with you for too long."],[1121,1296,"You're just an unwanted stray,"],[1304,1421,"yet you dare to yell"],[1421,1525,"in front of me?"],[1527,1627,"I'm telling you,"],[1629,1838,"when Andrew goes bankrupt,"],[1842,1967,"the first person I'll come for"],[1971,2058,"is you!"],[2216,2412,"My daddy won't go bankrupt!"],[2416,2566,"You're the ones who will go broke!"],[2795,2837,"Mr. Hayes,"],[2933,3131,"there's a dozen people downstairs."],[3212,3300,"They say"],[3304,3400,"they want you to pay with your life."],[3754,3862,"Hey, brat,"],[3866,3970,"aren't you supposed to be"],[3975,4070,"your daddy's lucky star?"],[4075,4200,"With such a huge crisis,"],[4201,4346,"how come you're useless now?"],[5027,5128,"Victor,"],[5229,5434,"I can bring you in on the deal."],[5845,5958,"I'll give you ten percent of the profits."],[5983,6115,"Ten percent?"],[6137,6329,"Do you take me for a beggar?"],[6375,6533,"I want"],[6537,6668,"fifty percent."],[6921,7041,"Impossible."],[7045,7175,"Fine."],[7179,7384,"If I can't get what I want,"],[7441,7608,"then nobody makes a dime."],[7670,7766,"Andrew,"],[7771,7954,"you'd better go discuss this"],[7958,8062,"with Sir Quinn."],[8604,8687,"Andrew,"],[8691,8787,"the workers are on strike."],[8791,8951,"I'm on my way to Mount Cloud."],[8954,9058,"What?"],[9062,9172,"I heard there were"],[9174,9275,"minor tremors on the mountain."],[9287,9425,"The news is spreading fast."],[9429,9570,"There's no way the project"],[9575,9720,"can continue."],[9790,9890,"Do we really"],[9902,10066,"have to compromise with Victor?"]],"56":[[119,229,"Andrew,"],[287,404,"I'm giving you a final"],[408,520,"ten minutes."],[566,670,"Once time is up,"],[777,920,"I won't wait another second."],[2441,2491,"Daddy,"],[2516,2705,"bad guys never win."],[2762,2870,"You're so good,"],[2891,3054,"you'll succeed at everything you do."],[3433,3520,"Succeed?"],[3537,3691,"Your dad will soon"],[3716,3804,"become my"],[3808,3920,"defeated opponent."],[4045,4120,"Andrew,"],[4145,4258,"time's up."],[4317,4454,"What have you decided?"],[4495,4558,"Andrew,"],[4616,4754,"either you come here right now"],[4767,4975,"and get on your knees to apologize,"],[4987,5087,"or else,"],[5116,5241,"just wait for that little company of yours"],[5283,5470,"to go bankrupt!"],[5919,6123,"No one is allowed to bully my daddy!"]],"57":[[390,445,"Andrew,"],[458,533,"great news!"],[558,627,"The two workers"],[631,712,"have been rescued."],[717,825,"Because of the tremors,"],[833,939,"we actually found"],[941,1033,"jade underground."],[1037,1154,"It's a blessing in disguise!"],[1587,1637,"Hello?"],[1929,1995,"What?"],[2066,2175,"The men were rescued,"],[2258,2350,"and at Mount Cloud,"],[2354,2475,"jade was found?"],[2516,2583,"What?"],[2937,3025,"How is that possible?"],[3095,3187,"Andrew,"],[3229,3337,"why do you always"],[3341,3445,"have such good luck?"],[3496,3666,"You always land on your feet."],[3808,3883,"You little brat,"],[3887,3954,"it was you."],[3996,4129,"You helped him!"],[4204,4320,"I told you already,"],[4359,4560,"heaven watches over my daddy."],[4606,4781,"He'll succeed in everything."],[5027,5087,"Victor,"],[5121,5179,"Brandon,"],[5196,5295,"you two are vicious."],[5308,5429,"You'll get karma!"],[5491,5566,"Victor,"],[5604,5733,"Mr. Quinn has already called the police."],[5785,5868,"The two workers"],[5871,5970,"will cooperate with the investigation."],[5975,6154,"Whether it was sabotage or an accident,"],[6173,6300,"I believe the authorities"],[6337,6466,"will give us justice."],[6550,6645,"Andrew,"],[6679,6787,"just you wait."],[6837,6920,"I definitely"],[6925,7054,"won't let you off easy!"]],"58":[[52,154,"Let's go."],[961,1150,"Seeing how panicked Victor looked,"],[1190,1287,"those two workers"],[1294,1420,"must have been bribed by him."],[1534,1613,"Jimmy,"],[1665,1758,"follow up on this."],[1781,1869,"You have to make sure those two"],[1871,1958,"tell the truth."],[1973,2062,"And contact our lawyer."],[2117,2237,"We're holding him accountable."],[2258,2291,"Yes, sir."],[2304,2345,"Mr. Hayes,"],[2492,2579,"once we prove Victor"],[2581,2687,"was the mastermind,"],[2791,2904,"he'll definitely go to jail."],[3038,3179,"He dug his own grave."],[3304,3416,"Regarding this incident,"],[3444,3537,"thanks to Emma,"],[3591,3725,"we were able to overcome it."],[3752,3870,"Emma really brings"],[3875,3983,"good luck to our family."],[4025,4129,"Anyone who adopts Emma"],[4141,4308,"is truly blessed."],[4348,4404,"Emma,"],[4508,4654,"you've helped Daddy again."],[4704,4770,"Thank you."],[4865,4995,"You're welcome, Daddy."],[5033,5187,"We're family."],[5246,5279,"All right."],[5325,5375,"Emma,"],[5454,5566,"go home with Grandma now."],[5620,5737,"I'll finish up my work here,"],[5750,5837,"then come home to join you."],[5862,5912,"Okay?"],[5927,5966,"Daddy,"],[5979,6108,"take care of yourself."],[6119,6237,"Don't work too hard."],[6300,6379,"Bye, Daddy."],[6433,6487,"Okay."],[6491,6566,"Bye."],[7329,7412,"The little brat is out."],[7413,7454,"Hurry, quick!"],[7850,7925,"Sharon,"],[7983,8120,"we've been tailing her all day,"],[8129,8279,"but haven't found a chance to strike."],[8970,9095,"Here's our chance."],[9175,9208,"Let's go."],[9500,9529,"Let's go."],[9991,10100,"Hey, little brat."],[10141,10266,"Long time no see."]],"59":[[157,320,"Auntie, you still dare to show up?"],[325,445,"Are you itching"],[450,570,"for another beating?"],[610,688,"You damn brat."],[704,764,"Today,"],[788,921,"no one can save you."],[923,1022,"Stop wasting your breath."],[1024,1123,"Just tie her up."],[1127,1204,"You big villains!"],[1212,1341,"You're not taking me anywhere."],[1537,1650,"You little brat,"],[1654,1854,"you sure talk big."],[1858,1930,"Stop!"],[2084,2209,"Grandma, don't be scared."],[2221,2375,"Bad people always get what they deserve."],[2383,2425,"You"],[2462,2633,"You've made my life miserable."],[2683,2764,"If anyone deserves retribution,"],[2767,2850,"it's going to hit you first,"],[2854,2991,"you little jinx!"],[3025,3096,"Tyler,"],[3100,3200,"tie them both up!"],[3295,3387,"Come here."],[3451,3525,"You villains!"],[3527,3708,"You won't get away with this."],[4384,4533,"Tyler, have you lost your mind?"],[4537,4620,"I told you to tie them up."],[4625,4744,"Why are you tying me up?"],[4819,4891,"Shut up."],[4952,5081,"You dare hit me?"],[5667,5750,"What's going on?"],[5808,5870,"Sharon,"],[5875,5991,"who tied you up?"],[6054,6125,"You idiot,"],[6175,6312,"I fell into that brat's trap."],[6315,6437,"Untie me, quickly!"],[6527,6570,"Let's go."],[6804,6929,"Trying to run?"],[7041,7160,"- Come here! - Let me go!"],[7162,7237,"Emma!"],[7273,7470,"Let go of me, you big bad guy!"],[7516,7679,"Help! Help!"]],"60":[[63,129,"Emma!"],[179,270,"You big bad guy!"],[295,429,"Emma! Emma!"],[489,604,"How dare you kidnap my daughter?"],[704,836,"You must have a death wish!"],[991,1100,"Andrew."],[1125,1237,"Take one more step,"],[1241,1411,"and I'll kill this little b*stard."],[1450,1516,"Daddy!"],[1520,1591,"Don't worry,"],[1595,1725,"Emma is going to be fine."],[1729,1789,"Andrew,"],[1792,1908,"I told you about this ages ago."],[1912,2050,"What took you so long?"],[2054,2129,"What?"],[2131,2185,"Don't tell me"],[2185,2279,"they knew all along"],[2283,2350,"that we were"],[2350,2450,"tailing them?"],[2454,2527,"Hey, Big Bad Guy,"],[2535,2694,"I spotted you ages ago."],[3262,3521,"They must be tired from tailing us all day."],[3529,3824,"Why not send them to have tea with the cops?"],[3896,3954,"Grandma,"],[3954,4150,"I want to call Daddy."],[4179,4258,"Okay."],[4691,4758,"Daddy,"],[4762,4937,"bad guys are following Emma."],[4941,5100,"Right at the company entrance."],[5104,5229,"Come quickly, okay?"],[5881,5973,"Grandma,"],[5977,6160,"wait here for Emma a moment."],[6166,6303,"Don't come over yet."],[6303,6395,"Alright."],[6841,6933,"Andrew,"],[6937,7066,"I've got the little brat."],[7069,7152,"Back off now!"],[7162,7304,"Or I'll strangle her!"],[7329,7370,"Emma!"],[7396,7471,"You d*mn brat!"],[7475,7579,"You really deserve to die."],[7595,7658,"Every time I see you,"],[7662,7762,"nothing good ever happens."],[7775,7837,"Back then,"],[7841,7962,"I shouldn't have brought you home"],[7966,8062,"from the orphanage!"],[8066,8158,"Sharon,"],[8179,8270,"you adopted Emma,"],[8275,8375,"but instead of caring for her,"],[8379,8533,"you're trying to kill her."],[8537,8608,"I think the one who deserves to die"],[8612,8720,"is actually you!"],[8725,8854,"If you come any closer,"],[8858,8962,"I'll choke her to death!"],[8966,9054,"Sharon!"],[9192,9362,"You want your son to be an orphan, don't you?"],[10113,10208,"You"],[10245,10366,"You little brat,"],[10370,10495,"I'm going to kill you."]],"61":[[1025,1087,"Emma."],[1144,1277,"Next time something like this happens,"],[1308,1463,"make sure to wait for Daddy"],[1492,1587,"before you act, okay?"],[1644,1700,"Daddy,"],[1704,1829,"I understand."],[1881,1956,"Andrew,"],[1964,2073,"thank God you're here."],[2084,2242,"I was scared to death."],[2321,2375,"Mr. Hayes."],[2383,2475,"Mr. Hayes, this is a misunderstanding."],[2483,2583,"It really is!"],[2638,2712,"It was all Sharon!"],[2756,2881,"She wanted to kidnap Emma."],[2889,3028,"It had nothing to do with me!"],[3150,3204,"Mr. Hayes,"],[3242,3392,"Tyler's the one who wanted money!"],[3398,3527,"I was forced to do it!"],[3542,3637,"You... you"],[3663,3767,"Neither of you"],[3783,3908,"is getting away with this."],[3910,4094,"Hand them over to the authorities."],[4167,4296,"Interrogate them thoroughly."],[4341,4420,"No, no"],[4458,4558,"Please, don't"],[4561,4678,"- Don't! - No, no!"],[4879,4958,"Those two"],[4960,5110,"really had some nerve."],[5113,5237,"Emma told me"],[5241,5433,"that they've been following us all day."],[5716,5750,"Emma,"],[5808,5933,"next time something like this happens,"],[5995,6104,"tell Daddy right away."],[6141,6237,"Okay?"],[6307,6375,"Okay."],[6619,6740,"I'll take you two home first."],[6794,6883,"Let's go, Emma."],[7004,7050,"Let's go."],[7641,7720,"Emma,"],[7765,7844,"are you alright?"],[7846,7941,"Let me check her."],[8141,8250,"Why is she so hot?"],[8329,8437,"She was terrified just now,"],[8545,8641,"and now she has a fever."],[8658,8770,"Amelia."],[8775,8872,"I'm okay."],[8983,9083,"Emma."],[9173,9231,"Andrew."],[9241,9352,"I've contacted my lawyer."],[9353,9450,"Don't worry."],[9454,9520,"As for those two,"],[9525,9658,"I'll make sure they rot in prison."],[9700,9844,"Daring to touch my granddaughter"],[9846,10020,"means crossing the Quinn family."],[10069,10164,"Andrew,"],[10167,10237,"leave this matter"],[10241,10362,"to the Quinn family."],[10366,10470,"You don't need to worry about it."],[10698,10810,"Mr. Quinn,"],[10820,10904,"there's something"],[11017,11141,"you might not know yet."],[11277,11362,"What is it?"]],"62":[[65,150,"Those two workers"],[175,281,"were very likely"],[283,454,"bribed by Victor and his son."],[550,633,"Mr. Quinn,"],[667,787,"I'm sorry to have dragged you into this."],[963,1096,"We're all family."],[1139,1235,"Don't talk about"],[1256,1404,"dragging us down."],[1422,1508,"Exactly."],[1519,1662,"We're partners in this."],[1674,1787,"Victor targeting you"],[1791,1922,"is crossing the Quinn family."],[1936,2062,"Victor is vicious."],[2071,2133,"If one plan fails,"],[2135,2233,"he'll definitely try another."],[2258,2300,"Andrew,"],[2312,2426,"you must stay on your guard."],[2477,2609,"Those two workers haven't woken up yet."],[2654,2737,"When they wake up"],[2741,2812,"and tell the truth,"],[2841,2975,"Victor and his son won't be able to escape."],[2985,3053,"I'm just afraid"],[3125,3233,"Victor"],[3251,3366,"will make sure they"],[3370,3487,"never wake up."],[3506,3604,"We must keep a strict guard"],[3625,3795,"at the hospital."],[3816,3883,"I understand."],[3941,4004,"Mr. Quinn,"],[4045,4125,"I plan to give that father and son"],[4129,4220,"something to do"],[4236,4337,"to keep them busy."],[4355,4458,"Have you"],[4462,4572,"come up with a plan?"],[4591,4670,"I found out"],[4690,4808,"Victor is selling fake medicine"],[4838,4958,"and forging customs documents."],[5091,5154,"Victor"],[5158,5279,"is such a bast*rd!"],[5295,5412,"Once this gets out,"],[5507,5620,"That should keep them busy for a while."],[5691,5837,"Victor, you sc*mbag,"],[5883,5962,"just to make money,"],[5983,6100,"you actually sold fake medicine."],[6141,6232,"I have to expose him."],[6258,6320,"Daddy,"],[6342,6412,"is that big baddie"],[6416,6541,"trying to go visit"],[6545,6770,"the police again?"],[6862,6975,"Emma, you're so smart."],[7062,7150,"Daddy,"],[7275,7430,"then you have to hurry"],[7475,7604,"and send the big baddie"],[7608,7754,"to the police station."],[7791,7858,"Okay."],[7920,8037,"Daddy will make the call right now"],[8054,8108,"to get the bad guy"],[8117,8181,"arrested."]],"63":[[91,220,"Make sure those two workers"],[225,358,"die in the hospital."],[362,537,"Leave no witnesses."],[575,700,"Once it's done,"],[704,870,"you'll be well rewarded."],[1237,1290,"Dad,"],[1292,1366,"bad news."],[1367,1496,"Something terrible happened."],[1634,1741,"Why are you so flustered?"],[1745,1850,"Pull yourself together."],[1871,1921,"Dad,"],[1941,2091,"our fake medicine business"],[2095,2254,"was leaked by someone,"],[2258,2387,"and the factory has been seized!"],[2504,2587,"What?"],[2633,2812,"Andrew must be behind this!"],[2927,3100,"That d*mn Andrew,"],[3107,3258,"why isn't he dead yet?"],[3331,3423,"Dad,"],[3440,3594,"I've received another piece"],[3608,3720,"of bad news."],[3737,3820,"Speak."],[4027,4198,"Andrew and his mother"],[4202,4313,"have both recovered."],[4315,4425,"The poison we used"],[4429,4583,"didn't work at all."],[4619,4720,"What?"],[5125,5258,"How is that possible?"],[5333,5457,"How did things"],[5459,5604,"slip out of my control?"],[5758,5837,"Listen."],[5869,6018,"No matter the cost,"],[6020,6120,"whatever the price,"],[6158,6358,"I want that wild brat dead!"],[6375,6433,"Dad,"],[6487,6570,"Sharon kidnapped"],[6575,6654,"that wild brat,"],[6658,6770,"but Andrew already sent her"],[6775,6933,"to rot in prison."],[6937,7043,"At a time like this,"],[7087,7250,"They'll definitely be on high alert."],[7525,7604,"You useless fool!"],[7633,7808,"You can't even handle a simple task."],[8229,8343,"Go make the arrangements."],[8359,8488,"I'll get someone to coordinate with you"],[8491,8608,"from the inside."],[8654,8758,"This time,"],[8762,8870,"I'm going to kill"],[8875,8987,"that wild brat!"],[8991,9070,"Dad,"],[9141,9262,"who is this person"],[9341,9420,"you're talking about?"]],"64":[[12,104,"Dad,"],[144,252,"who is that person"],[319,404,"you mentioned?"],[433,587,"Don't ask questions you shouldn't."],[625,712,"Get out!"],[1429,1500,"Do it."],[2029,2120,"Grandpa,"],[2250,2379,"Emma is here."],[2475,2537,"Mr. Quinn,"],[2548,2667,"you called Emma over so urgently."],[2679,2813,"Is there a problem with the project?"],[2958,3087,"The project is fine."],[3091,3280,"I just want Emma to help me with something."],[3395,3556,"Grandpa doesn't trust us anymore."],[3570,3758,"He wants Emma to choose the proposal."],[3783,3845,"Whatever Emma picks"],[3852,3920,"is sure to be the right choice."],[3923,3969,"Yeah."],[4012,4093,"Grandpa,"],[4104,4291,"I'm still just a little kid,"],[4320,4483,"I don't know how to pick a proposal."],[4506,4570,"Mr. Quinn,"],[4608,4708,"selecting a proposal"],[4709,4812,"is a serious matter."],[4819,4978,"We should let the professionals handle it."],[5004,5068,"Oh,"],[5158,5279,"the two managers"],[5283,5383,"in charge of the project"],[5404,5500,"have been fighting endlessly"],[5504,5637,"over the plan."],[5658,5718,"Emma,"],[5731,5862,"just pick one at random."],[5879,5937,"Even if"],[5958,6028,"you get it wrong,"],[6033,6118,"it doesn't matter."],[6141,6283,"Just go ahead and choose."],[6341,6404,"Emma,"],[6458,6516,"pick whichever you want."],[6554,6641,"Grandpa won't blame you."],[6664,6762,"Alright, come on."]],"65":[[663,729,"Grandpa,"],[740,864,"I've made my choice."],[950,1079,"You're amazing, Emma."],[1265,1354,"We'll go with this plan."],[1362,1404,"Good."],[1425,1537,"Make the arrangements."],[1554,1629,"Yes, sir."],[1741,1850,"Emma"],[1854,1945,"is really smart."],[1961,2058,"Amelia will take you"],[2062,2177,"to get some bubble tea, okay?"],[2191,2304,"Thank you, Amelia."],[2341,2425,"Thanks for the trouble, Miss Quinn."],[2512,2591,"Bye, Grandpa."],[2604,2670,"Bye, Dad."],[2745,2887,"Bye."],[3358,3416,"Amelia."],[3529,3591,"Ethan."],[3595,3674,"What are you doing here?"],[3691,3775,"I'm off today."],[3798,3892,"Where are you and Emma going?"],[3904,3965,"I'll give you a ride."],[3971,4105,"I'm taking Emma to get bubble tea."],[4135,4227,"I know a bubble tea place"],[4229,4287,"that's really good."],[4291,4337,"Get in."],[4341,4413,"I'll take you there."],[4416,4464,"Okay!"],[4516,4587,"Let's go, Emma."]],"66":[[87,174,"What about mine?"],[645,702,"Ethan,"],[723,819,"didn't you say you were taking us"],[819,912,"to get bubble tea?"],[945,1045,"Why are we driving so far off course?"],[1187,1264,"Just wait a little longer."],[1287,1387,"We're almost there."],[1512,1608,"Amelia,"],[1616,1720,"he's lying to you."],[1812,1858,"Emma,"],[1891,2008,"Uncle isn't lying."],[2116,2183,"Uncle,"],[2212,2300,"people who tell lies"],[2304,2454,"are going to have really bad luck."],[3033,3087,"Ethan,"],[3112,3187,"where on earth are you taking"],[3191,3262,"Emma and me?"],[3625,3687,"Amelia,"],[3704,3812,"the doors are locked."],[3819,3908,"You can't escape."],[3937,4012,"You big bad guy!"],[4019,4191,"How dare you bully Amelia!"],[4229,4387,"You'll be punished for this!"],[4412,4476,"Ethan,"],[4514,4629,"how much is that person paying you?"],[4645,4712,"I'll pay double"],[4725,4812,"if you let Emma and me go."],[4837,4987,"You can't afford double the price."],[5012,5116,"Because the Quinn family's money"],[5119,5245,"will soon be all mine."],[5966,6120,"I want to find my daddy!"],[7491,7579,"Emma! Emma!"],[7596,7660,"Get up, quick!"],[7662,7761,"I'll take you to find your dad."],[7924,7999,"Amelia!"],[8000,8058,"Today, I'm going to"],[8062,8154,"break one of your legs,"],[8162,8262,"and see how you escape then!"]],"67":[[219,304,"You big bad guy!"],[308,507,"Don't hurt Amelia!"],[879,954,"Emma, quick!"],[958,1088,"- Let's go! - Hurry!"],[1455,1556,"Where do you think you're going?"],[1567,1649,"Hand it over."],[1675,1753,"Come here."],[1763,1837,"Let go of Emma!"],[1840,1927,"- Amelia! - Amelia!"],[1929,2015,"Get lost!"],[2079,2208,"Amelia!"],[2293,2450,"- You won't get away with this! - You little brat,"],[2458,2554,"I'll tape your mouth shut,"],[2558,2683,"and see how you escape then."],[3175,3266,"Tie them up!"],[3270,3375,"Let go of me!"],[3377,3458,"Ethan!"],[3461,3606,"What you're doing is illegal!"],[3629,3750,"What took you guys so long?"],[3754,3806,"Let go!"],[3806,3923,"They almost got away."],[4206,4303,"Let me go!"],[4305,4420,"The brat and Amelia"],[4425,4608,"have been tied up."],[4612,4745,"You can make your move now."],[4854,4938,"Mr. Quinn."],[4958,5021,"I'll go out and see"],[5025,5125,"why Emma isn't back yet."],[5320,5412,"Andrew,"],[5416,5579,"you really are a doting father."],[5608,5654,"Alright."],[5658,5780,"I'll go down with you to check."],[5990,6120,"Emma and Amelia have been kidnapped!"],[6306,6380,"What did you say?"]],"68":[[45,162,"Ethan called me"],[212,320,"and demanded a ransom."],[1227,1295,"Victor,"],[1337,1479,"did you kidnap Emma and Miss Quinn?"],[1491,1575,"Andrew,"],[1583,1729,"whoever crosses me"],[1758,1950,"has to pay the price."],[2083,2219,"Emma and Miss Quinn are innocent."],[2231,2341,"If you have a problem, come at me."],[2373,2454,"Let them go."],[2479,2575,"Andrew,"],[2589,2698,"you caused me"],[2698,2820,"so much trouble."],[2825,2937,"For this loss,"],[2987,3120,"you're paying me back."],[3271,3371,"Get lost!"],[3935,3987,"Mr. Quinn,"],[4058,4207,"Ethan and Victor are working together."],[4408,4483,"Victor"],[4487,4612,"is insidious and cunning."],[4644,4712,"Until he gets what he wants,"],[4727,4837,"he won't stop."],[4875,4929,"We"],[4958,5070,"can't act rashly."],[5095,5170,"Mr. Quinn,"],[5181,5285,"I'll go find Victor first"],[5291,5379,"to distract him."],[5420,5516,"Please send more people"],[5523,5662,"to find Emma and Miss Quinn."],[5725,5775,"Andrew,"],[5808,5933,"Emma and Amelia"],[5966,6070,"are both my granddaughters."],[6108,6200,"I promise I won't"],[6204,6295,"let anything happen to them."],[6341,6420,"Alright."],[6425,6520,"I'll head out now."]],"69":[[16,187,"Tell the Quinn family to prepare more ransom."],[225,291,"Once I get the money,"],[325,441,"I'm leaving this place"],[470,545,"to lay low."],[702,756,"Ethan!"],[790,912,"I'm the one you're after."],[941,1037,"Let Emma go now."],[1041,1150,"She's just a child."],[1216,1291,"A child?"],[1304,1412,"She's got plenty of tricks."],[1433,1537,"And let her go tip someone off?"],[1541,1570,"You"],[1683,1791,"This kid is weird as hell."],[1798,1866,"We can't let her go."],[1871,2029,"And don't take the tape off her mouth."],[2052,2170,"Whatever she says comes true."],[2195,2258,"If something happens,"],[2279,2370,"we're all screwed."],[2541,2712,"She's only a child!"],[2725,2871,"You even have her hands and feet tied!"],[2875,2960,"What could she possibly do?"],[2971,3083,"Take the tape off her mouth right now."],[3091,3166,"I'm telling you,"],[3170,3314,"if anything happens to Emma,"],[3321,3472,"you won't get a single cent."],[4010,4070,"Ethan,"],[4081,4170,"this kid is so cute."],[4186,4324,"Let's take the tape off."],[4437,4495,"Don't!"],[4587,4670,"Are you okay?"],[4695,4845,"You're a kidnapper!"],[5145,5229,"You damn brat."],[5266,5387,"You think staring at me like that"],[5425,5483,"will make me"],[5594,5774,"Aww, I'll take the tape off for you."],[5779,5854,"No!"],[5916,5987,"Don't do it!"]],"70":[[11,57,"Let go."],[475,608,"I'll say this one last time,"],[641,798,"don't take the tape off her mouth."],[800,904,"Her jinxed little mouth"],[931,1070,"will be the end of us all."],[1319,1407,"Watch her."],[1491,1633,"I'm stepping out to take a call."],[2049,2106,"D*mn it."],[2162,2266,"He actually hit me."],[2281,2378,"You asked for it."],[2429,2594,"Forgot how jinxed that kid is?"],[3006,3153,"You two silly uncles."],[3153,3243,"Bet you didn't see that coming."],[3253,3389,"Even with my mouth taped,"],[3397,3537,"I can still untie the ropes."],[4142,4250,"Listen, fellas."],[4266,4400,"If you let us go,"],[4404,4491,"the Quinn family's money,"],[4495,4581,"I'll give it all to you."],[4585,4670,"None of it goes to Ethan."],[4675,4750,"What do you say?"],[4983,5112,"I'm Miss Quinn."],[5145,5189,"Emma"],[5191,5337,"is Andrew's precious daughter."],[5387,5508,"We're both worth a fortune."],[5545,5729,"She makes a good point."],[5741,5833,"But if Ethan finds out,"],[5844,5979,"we're dead meat."],[6016,6133,"Please, fellas."],[6140,6283,"You saw what happened earlier."],[6287,6420,"The bad blood between me and Ethan Scumbag."],[6445,6500,"As for my money,"],[6504,6608,"I won't give him a single dime."],[6612,6700,"Amelia,"],[6723,6875,"don't try any tricks."],[6925,7029,"My fists"],[7033,7170,"aren't just for show."],[7183,7354,"I'm just a helpless woman."],[7370,7485,"I can't outrun you,"],[7485,7612,"and I definitely can't fight you."],[7616,7770,"We just want to live."],[7775,7920,"Uncles,"],[7975,8185,"I'll be good."],[8188,8345,"I promise I won't run away."],[8454,8570,"How can you talk?"]],"71":[[108,266,"It was the uncle on the left"],[270,508,"who took the tape off for me."],[538,596,"That's right."],[600,683,"It was me."],[716,870,"Uncles,"],[875,979,"please let Emma go,"],[983,1108,"okay?"],[1156,1250,"Emma knows"],[1254,1395,"you're both good people."],[1404,1500,"Why are you standing there?"],[1608,1741,"Hurry up and tape her mouth shut!"],[2737,2785,"I can't go through"],[2790,2862,"with this deal anymore."],[3064,3172,"That's Emma for you."],[3192,3418,"A few words made the kidnapper feel guilty."],[3516,3620,"Are you out of your mind?"],[3627,3695,"Look at her."],[3715,3820,"She's so cute,"],[3827,3908,"and so sensible."],[3925,4008,"Let's let her go."],[4031,4162,"I can't bring myself to do it."],[4208,4297,"What guilt?"],[4320,4420,"I don't believe it."],[4433,4590,"I won't let a little girl outsmart me."],[5262,5370,"I'm really a piece of sh*t."]],"72":[[146,200,"You guys"],[497,583,"I told you to"],[587,675,"tape the little brat's"],[679,770,"mouth shut!"],[787,920,"Why did you tape your own mouth?"],[975,1024,"Useless!"],[1037,1129,"A bunch of useless trash!"],[1198,1302,"You little brat,"],[1331,1454,"I'm going to teach you a lesson."],[1550,1712,"Help!"],[2179,2304,"I've had enough of you!"],[2395,2486,"You dare hit me?"],[2543,2661,"You haven't got a shred of dignity!"],[2941,3070,"You dare hit me again?"],[3125,3241,"Don't you want to get paid?"],[3248,3342,"Screw the money!"],[3356,3460,"I just don't like your face!"],[3666,3720,"Hit him!"],[3725,3800,"Keep hitting him!"],[3804,3879,"Good hit!"],[3883,3987,"Beat him till he can't get up!"],[3995,4125,"I'll add another $200,000!"],[4611,4784,"- Stop hitting me! - Oh God, it's loose."],[5225,5425,"Stop hitting!"],[5646,5788,"Why won't it untie?"],[6135,6241,"Stop it!"],[6733,6787,"Let's go."],[7001,7136,"Help!"],[7225,7341,"Dad, I'm here!"],[7415,7504,"Emma!"],[8217,8357,"How dare you bully my daughter!"],[8404,8475,"Get them!"],[8583,8683,"Bodyguard uncles,"],[8696,8821,"he's the big bad guy!"],[9037,9220,"Why is it always me getting hurt?"]],"73":[[25,104,"We're sorry!"],[123,272,"We'll never do anything bad again."],[279,371,"From now on,"],[382,500,"we'll turn over a new leaf"],[516,604,"and serve society."],[638,738,"Uncles,"],[750,845,"admitting your mistakes"],[847,1012,"makes you good people again."],[1142,1212,"Mr. Hayes,"],[1219,1348,"it was Victor and Ethan"],[1348,1497,"who told us to kidnap Miss Emma."],[1558,1637,"Mr. Hayes,"],[1641,1766,"I recorded the calls"],[1770,1886,"we had with Victor."],[1918,2072,"I'll send you the audio right now."],[2145,2237,"Dad,"],[2287,2504,"these Uncles want to be good."],[2508,2675,"Please give them a chance,"],[2675,2762,"okay?"],[2975,3050,"Alright."],[3104,3250,"Since my Emma asked,"],[3404,3563,"I'll give you one more chance."],[3654,3804,"Testify against Victor for me,"],[3861,4019,"and I'll hire a lawyer to defend you."],[4096,4195,"Thank you, Mr. Hayes!"],[4200,4283,"Thank you, Miss Hayes!"],[4287,4412,"I'll never be a bad guy again!"],[4420,4555,"Thank you, thank you!"],[5179,5275,"Sir Quinn,"],[5941,5983,"since"],[5987,6195,"you want to work with our company,"],[6216,6378,"I'll give you a chance."],[6408,6571,"Sign this contract."],[6579,6696,"I'm sure"],[6700,6900,"Miss Quinn will be very happy."],[7233,7345,"Victor,"],[7350,7470,"you really are despicable."],[7508,7620,"Cut the cr*p."],[7621,7733,"Just sign it already!"],[8954,9004,"Really?"],[9091,9158,"Grandpa,"],[9162,9262,"don't sign it!"],[9281,9366,"Benjamin!"],[9382,9539,"Do you want to get your sister killed?"],[9562,9641,"Victor,"],[9667,9809,"you'd better check the news."],[10204,10304,"What?"],[10408,10533,"How could this happen?"],[10543,10641,"Head back to the office immediately."],[10641,10697,"Let's go."],[10701,10847,"Move! Hurry up!"]],"74":[[484,544,"Dad,"],[562,700,"the news about our company selling fake medicine"],[705,837,"has blown up everywhere."],[839,914,"Right now, downstairs,"],[916,1050,"a bunch of angry customers are gathering,"],[1054,1210,"demanding an explanation."],[1248,1394,"Dad, you have to think of something!"],[1417,1567,"What am I supposed to do?!"],[1595,1720,"It's all because you're useless."],[1725,1804,"I told you to kidnap someone,"],[1808,1912,"and you couldn't even manage that!"],[2034,2171,"Didn't you arrange the people"],[2191,2300,"who kidnapped the brat?"],[2492,2629,"You dare talk back to me?"],[2629,2787,"Go get me a lawyer immediately!"],[2912,2981,"Dad,"],[2981,3062,"please calm down."],[3066,3212,"I'll go find a lawyer right now."],[3266,3437,"Get me the best lawyer."],[3441,3620,"We can't afford to lose this case!"],[4450,4508,"Andrew,"],[4512,4579,"Emma,"],[4583,4720,"you're finally back."],[4750,4866,"You scared me to death."],[5241,5329,"Grandma,"],[5333,5450,"I'm okay."],[5454,5579,"The big bad guys have already been"],[5583,5754,"taken away by the police."],[5866,5937,"Andrew,"],[5987,6096,"regarding Victor,"],[6098,6188,"how is the investigation going?"],[6233,6329,"It's all clear."],[6333,6492,"Victor is suspected of selling fakes"],[6498,6608,"and forging customs documents."],[6654,6746,"The two kidnappers"],[6750,6862,"have turned state's witness."],[6921,7016,"They'll testify against Victor."],[7038,7129,"He won't get away this time."],[7195,7279,"That's good."],[7325,7441,"We must get justice for Emma."],[7445,7562,"To seek justice."],[7658,7766,"Emma,"],[7770,7904,"you stay home with Grandma."],[7908,8025,"Dad needs to take care of something."],[8029,8104,"Okay?"],[8312,8400,"Dad,"],[8404,8633,"I want to go with you."],[8762,8889,"Emma is still shaken up."],[8908,9054,"She feels safe with you,"],[9058,9191,"so take her with you."],[9658,9779,"Okay."],[9783,9850,"Come here."],[9962,10048,"Emma,"],[10052,10212,"come with Dad."],[10229,10428,"I'll take you to see a big show."],[10441,10508,"Dad,"],[10512,10745,"what kind of show is it?"],[10904,11020,"It's a show about"],[11025,11112,"the big bad guy"],[11116,11287,"getting caught."]],"75":[[579,679,"My grandma fell into a coma"],[681,791,"after taking the medicine"],[795,896,"produced by your company!"],[898,964,"You heartless crooks!"],[967,1035,"Selling fake medicine!"],[1037,1129,"You're killing people for money!"],[1133,1181,"Victor,"],[1183,1331,"- You must give us an answer today! - Yeah!"],[1333,1460,"You must give us an answer!"],[1461,1525,"Give us an answer!"],[1529,1761,"Everyone,"],[1779,1879,"please calm down."],[1883,2024,"Just listen to me."],[2091,2279,"Someone counterfeited our trademark"],[2346,2479,"and sold fake, unregulated drugs"],[2483,2583,"to make a profit."],[2587,2750,"We're victims here, too!"],[2839,2964,"Someone is spreading rumors"],[2969,3108,"and maliciously slandering our company."],[3175,3320,"I've already hired a lawyer"],[3325,3429,"to investigate this thoroughly,"],[3462,3612,"and I'll give everyone an explanation."],[3625,3716,"We don't believe you!"],[3720,3820,"You must give us an answer!"],[3825,3908,"Is that so?"],[4425,4520,"You big bad guy!"],[4525,4683,"You've done so many bad things."],[4687,4826,"You're going to get what you deserve!"],[4896,5092,"Emma is absolutely right."],[5108,5275,"Repeated injustice"],[5279,5391,"leads to certain doom."],[5437,5509,"Andrew,"],[5554,5662,"the one spreading malicious rumors about us"],[5666,5762,"is you!"]],"76":[[16,142,"You counterfeited our trademark,"],[148,333,"and you're the one selling unregulated goods!"],[408,508,"Look, everyone,"],[558,694,"the one actually selling fake drugs"],[698,779,"is him!"],[1137,1227,"You're lying!"],[1229,1397,"My dad is a good person."],[1421,1612,"He would never do something like that."],[1950,2067,"He's your dad,"],[2073,2219,"so of course you'd take his side."],[2315,2431,"Brandon,"],[2436,2602,"you claim I sell unregulated goods,"],[2677,2760,"but do you have proof?"],[2908,3081,"Just wait until I find the evidence."],[3083,3245,"I'll make sure you never recover."],[3350,3453,"You can't produce any evidence,"],[3548,3662,"but I can."],[3754,3875,"Jimmy,"],[3889,4054,"show everyone the evidence!"],[4477,4536,"What is this?"],[4548,4615,"Look at this."],[4752,4827,"Th-this"],[4879,4997,"this looks real."],[5033,5164,"- Exactly. - It's all real."],[5200,5258,"It really is."],[5329,5433,"Let me see"],[5437,5570,"what kind of evidence you have."],[6054,6125,"How is this possible?"]],"77":[[17,112,"It's him! That's the guy!"],[154,254,"How is this possible?"],[325,354,"Dad"],[395,462,"What are you looking at?"],[725,808,"Brandon!"],[837,970,"Look what you've done!"],[995,1129,"You've completely ruined me!"],[1146,1187,"Dad?"],[1213,1318,"What did I do now?"],[1354,1479,"You have the nerve to ask?"],[1485,1688,"See for yourself what's written here!"],[2240,2299,"Impossible."],[2375,2500,"How did they trace this back to me?"],[2541,2637,"Brandon."],[2654,2850,"Nothing stays hidden forever."],[2896,2995,"You lined your own pockets,"],[3000,3070,"sold substandard goods,"],[3075,3154,"and showed no regard for human life."],[3191,3354,"You are absolutely unforgivable."],[3440,3602,"You crooks deserve to die!"],[3619,3706,"Victor, Brandon,"],[3712,3791,"I've already called the police."],[3791,3905,"Get ready to rot in jail."],[3908,4000,"The evidence is irrefutable."],[4004,4104,"You can't escape now."],[4138,4278,"Don't let them get away!"],[4702,4754,"Daddy,"],[4808,4933,"they look so miserable."],[5025,5100,"Emma,"],[5141,5258,"that's because they did terrible things."],[5304,5370,"Bad guys"],[5450,5550,"never come to a good end."],[5612,5658,"Daddy,"],[5683,5787,"from now on, I'll be"],[5791,5937,"a good, obedient girl."],[6008,6091,"Good."],[6150,6254,"You're such a good girl, Emma."]],"78":[[425,487,"Grandma,"],[512,759,"here's a birthday present from me."],[845,1037,"I wish you endless happiness"],[1041,1137,"and a long, healthy life."],[1175,1304,"Thank you, Emma."],[1466,1695,"Emma is so thoughtful."],[1800,1862,"Emma,"],[1866,1970,"we actually need to thank you"],[1975,2124,"for curing Amelia's love-struck brain."],[2254,2321,"Bro,"],[2323,2490,"stop bringing up my dark past."],[2491,2600,"It's so embarrassing."],[2604,2691,"Amelia,"],[2695,2808,"you will definitely meet"],[2841,2991,"your Prince Charming,"],[3025,3229,"and live happily ever after."],[3370,3500,"Thank you, Emma."],[3533,3695,"I love you so much."],[3975,4144,"Victor and Brandon"],[4148,4229,"getting arrested"],[4233,4387,"was really satisfying."],[4462,4529,"Andrew,"],[4573,4635,"I heard"],[4650,4791,"that all their company shares"],[4795,4966,"were acquired by you at a low price."]],"79":[[40,141,"With the company reorganized,"],[187,291,"all the shares"],[325,450,"have been transferred to Emma's name."],[508,645,"You gave them all to Emma?"],[715,806,"If it weren't for Emma,"],[950,1126,"I wouldn't have anything I have today."],[1395,1570,"It's what you deserve."],[1654,1741,"So,"],[1783,1916,"regarding the project revenue,"],[1959,2091,"I also plan to give Emma"],[2095,2266,"thirty percent of the profits."],[2350,2495,"Without Emma's help,"],[2516,2629,"how could our partnership"],[2665,2870,"have gone so smoothly?"],[3025,3179,"Emma is so young,"],[3183,3337,"yet she's already a little rich girl."],[3545,3698,"I don't want money."],[3700,3840,"I just want to be with everyone"],[3840,3987,"forever."],[4362,4420,"Emma."],[4483,4525,"Come here."],[4741,4808,"Emma,"],[4888,5030,"I'm so happy to have met you."],[5104,5252,"I will protect you forever."],[5454,5595,"I'm also happy"],[5600,5712,"to meet you, Daddy."],[5941,6029,"Emma,"],[6258,6470,"up we go!"]]}